node.text: obsessed with fleet ilya’s natural leather pieces that i cant afford so i drew some stuff this comfy monday✨ censored just in case cause I don’t usually post any nude art or studies! Here’s to hoping it doesn’t get buried so please leave a like or comment if you want to support my work! Saving and sharing also always helps (:

node.text: Much requested, the final girl, Bloom ✨ swipe to see them all together finally😤 !! Im so happy with how they all turned out, thank you all the new people who discovered my work through these fan arts! Now i need to start a new project hahaa. What are you hoping to see me work on?
